{"tid":1420963,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[明星老闆公開譴責示威者是錯的]香港人請全面抵制《華嫂冰室》及《華星冰室》","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T08:54:15.000Z","uid":15086,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ed955d58d756978a8b1f79eafe1fcefbdb6b31","tid":1420963,"uid":15086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"余文樂為《華嫂冰室》大股東及公然責罵示威者一切行為<br />\n而元朗華嫂冰室亦是牛屎佬出身<br />\n懷疑與元朗白衫黑幫關係千絲萬縷<br />\n應該讓更多香港及台灣人知道及抵制<br />\n<br />\n直至代表發言人道歉或交代為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hu32h5G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHu32h5G.jpg&h=16fa8e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vBLfXw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vBLfXw.jpg&h=2bf4db79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚校長及莊思敏為《華星冰室》超級大股東<br />\n而譚校長強烈支持警方以非人道暴力執法<br />\n莊思敏則是爆波姿態強烈譴責示威者一齊行為<br />\n更可恥的是<br />\n在全民打算抵制華嫂冰室的時候，《華星冰室》打手自己衝出黎柒扮晒黃，俾人篤爆大老細亦是非常深藍， 只為錢變成牆頭草兩邊擺，成為過街老鼠之日指日可待<br />\n<br />\n應該讓更多香港及台灣遊客知道及抵制<br />\n<br />\n直至代表發言人道歉或交代為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzgbVWo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzgbVWo.jpg&h=ef8ff53f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzeEkn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzeEkn4.jpg&h=46829127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00ca9c4fd66bd312813f089e8ff723289c15456e","tid":1420963,"uid":15086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"不要以為以離地之處屌香港人老母是沒有代價的"},{"pid":"d094ff067b189ae46e7574a94e77f4f44bb2ce2d","tid":1420963,"uid":187398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"推到佢執"},{"pid":"4c4a00cada0478e1dfa930cf2a610d25c3ad6898","tid":1420963,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"返工附近有間<br />\n唔會再食了 仆街華嫂"},{"pid":"84e6e8d0dd01a2f29746cacc579e9